items.title: Melianthus comosus
items.content_text: Very hardy weed that has colonised along the edges of the Sutherland's Creek south of Steiglitz. Infestations of multiple patches along creek, from 5 to 100s of plants. Photos taken by Jo Day.

items.title: Grevillea rosmarinifolia hybrids
items.content_text: A natural hybrid between Grevillea rosmarinifolia and G. chrysophaea. Habit similar to G. rosmarinifolia from this area, being low shrub. Only a few plants observed here. More common hybrid form here of these two species is taller, open shrub similar in form to G. chrysophaea.
